OL,3,CRiver Thames site among 13 proposed
OL,4,Cnew swimming spots
OL,6,FThe first official bathing spot on the
OL,7,FRiver Thames is among 13 new
OL,8,Fdesignated swimming sites proposed by
OL,9,Fthe Government.
OL,11,FOthers include popular beaches, a
OL,12,Fmeadow and river site in the area that
OL,13,Finspired The Wind In The Willows, and
OL,14,Fa spot in Yorkshire where the River
OL,15,FSwale flows in waterfalls over
OL,16,Flimestone steps.
