OL,3,CRiver Thames site among 13 proposed
OL,4,Cnew swimming spots
OL,6,FThe first designated bathing spot on
OL,7,Fthe Thames would mark a "vast
OL,8,Ftransformation" in water quality in
OL,9,Fthe river which was declared
OL,10,Fbiologically dead in the 1950s due to
OL,11,Fpollution, officials said.
OL,13,FDesignation would mean sites are
OL,14,Fsubject to regular water quality
OL,15,Ftesting, giving people a better idea
OL,16,Fof the state of the water they are
OL,17,Fswimming, paddling or enjoying water
OL,18,Fsports in.
