OL,3,CRiver Thames site among 13 proposed
OL,4,Cnew swimming spots
OL,6,FCommunities and campaigners in some
OL,7,Fareas hope it will increase pressure
OL,8,Ffor efforts to clean up their local
OL,9,Frivers and coasts.
OL,11,FThe Government said the plans would
OL,12,Fincrease the number of England's
OL,13,Fofficial bathing sites to 464 beaches,
OL,14,Fcoastal stretches, rivers and lakes.
OL,16,FWater minister Emma Hardy said:
OL,17,F"Rivers and beaches are at the heart
OL,18,Fof so many communities, where people
OL,19,Fcome together, families make memories
OL,20,Fand swimmers of all ages feel the
OL,21,Fbenefits of being outdoors safely.
