OL,3,CRiver Thames site among 13 proposed
OL,4,Cnew swimming spots
OL,6,F"Our plans to designate new bathing
OL,7,Fwater sites show how we are backing
OL,8,Flocal ambition and recognising the
OL,9,Fpride in places that matter most to
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,F"This comes alongside this
OL,13,FGovernment's generational reform of
OL,14,Fthe water system that will cut water
OL,15,Fpollution and clean up our rivers
OL,16,Flakes and seas for good."
