OL,12,Fpopular with locals;
OL,14,F` Newton and Noss Creeks, Devon ` a
OL,15,Fnarrow tidal inlet just off the River
OL,16,FYealm in the South Devon Area of
OL,17,FOutstanding Natural Beauty;
OL,19,F` Canvey Island Foreshore, Essex ` a
OL,20,Ffamily-favourite sandy beach;
